<p>Congrats <%= @company.name %>!</p>

<p>You have a new user who's requested to join your company. Click the following click to approve them, or visit your company dashboard.</p>

<p>Some info on your new user:</p>

<p>Name: <%= @user.name %><br />
Email: <%= @user.email %><br />
Title: <%= @user.employee_title.name %><br />
Signed up on: <%= @user.created_at %></p>

<!-- TODO: for some reason, adding another param here prepens a &amp; onto the email -->
<%= link_to "Approve", 
edit_account_approval_url(@user.approval_token, email: @user.email) %>